text: Annette Wyrwoll (born 14 November 1955) is a German equestrian. She competed in the individual eventing at the 2000 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1955 births Category:Living people Category:German female equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Germany Category:Equestrians at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:People from Neuwied
